reviewText: This is the best acted, most realistic and most inspiring MOSES (and 10 commandments) retelling I have ever watched. I have given several as gifts, especially for this upcoming Passover Season (the story of the EXODUS)
Follows the Bible..used it for a Sunday School class
I love it and it's right in line with the truth in the Bible
I liked this version the best of moses movies I have ever seen.  I really like his performance
